name: BigTimesTableDuel
0:
”Alexa, start big times table duel”
”this is thirty nine”
”what is the score”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: big times table duel
des:
Who can calculate the times table from 11 to 19 the fastest?

Alexa asks you to solve multiplications of the big times table , such as '15 times 7', and the player must calculate the answer: '105'.

You can test your calculation skills alone or play against any number of players. You either answer in turn or you can optionally use your Alexa Game Buttons (whoever presses first may answer).

Whoever has 5 points first wins. But attention, wrong answers lead to negative points.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
